<div class="authi">
<img class="authicn vm" id="authicon2027039" src="static/image/common/online_member.gif" />
<em id="authorposton2027039"> يوللىغان ۋاقتى  2015-3-9 08:09:22 PM</em>
<span class="pipe">|</span><a href="http://bbs.misranim.com/thread-135916-6-1.html" rel="nofollow">ھەممە قەۋەتنى كۆرۈش</a>
<span class="pipe">|</span>
